///Take Full Screen Shot///////////
----------------------------------
✅ 1. Using Google Chrome (Built-in – No Extension)
Steps:
Open your webpage in Chrome
Press Ctrl + Shift + I (open Developer Tools)
Press Ctrl + Shift + P
Type: screenshot
Click: Capture full size screenshot

👉 It will automatically download the full page image.

✅ 2. Using Mozilla Firefox (Very Easy)
Steps:
Right-click anywhere on the page
Click Take Screenshot
Select Save full page

👉 Super simple, no extra tools needed.

